templates.name: Fusion Apps BIP to ADW Incremental Load Template (Customer Managed)
templates.description: Application that allows Fusion Apps BI Publisher reports to run extracts based on and report the last execution in a metadata table stored in an Autonomous Data Warehouse target schema.

templates.name: Oracle Vision Image Template
templates.description: Application with REST tasks for performing OCI Vision Image Analysis. The tasks include image classification, image object detection, and image text detection.

templates.name: Oracle Vision Document Template
templates.description: Application with REST tasks for performing OCI Vision Document AI. The tasks include document classification, document key value detection, document language classification, document table detection, and document text detection.

templates.name: Oracle Object Store Management Template
templates.description: Application with REST tasks for Object Storage to copy, delete, and rename objects and to create and delete buckets

templates.name: Oracle DataSafe Masking Template
templates.description: Application with parameterized tasks to generate a Data Safe sensitive model and masking from a target Oracle database schema.

templates.name: Oracle DB to ADW Incremental Load Template (Customer Managed)
templates.description: Application that allows incremental tasks to run based on and report the last execution in a metadata table stored in an Autonomous Data Warehouse target schema.

templates.name: Load Files from Oracle Object Store into ADW
templates.description: Application with tasks to load different file types from OCI Object Storage into Autonomous Data Warehouse: JSON, Parquet, CSV, Avro.
